# nested-prefix-entries-each-level

## Input

```
 a {
 1 1
 b {
   2 2
   c {
  3 3
  }
 }
 }

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..45
  SPACE@0..1 " "
  PREFIX_BLOCK@1..45
    WORD_KEY@1..2
      WORD@1..2 "a"
    SPACE@2..3 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@3..4 "{"
    NEWLINE@4..5 "\n"
    SPACE@5..6 " "
    ENTRY@6..10
      WORD_KEY@6..7
        WORD@6..7 "1"
      SPACE@7..8 " "
      INTEGER@8..9
        NUMERAL@8..9 "1"
      NEWLINE@9..10 "\n"
    SPACE@10..11 " "
    PREFIX_BLOCK@11..42
      WORD_KEY@11..12
        WORD@11..12 "b"
      SPACE@12..13 " "
      OPEN_BRACE@13..14 "{"
      NEWLINE@14..15 "\n"
      SPACE@15..18 "   "
      ENTRY@18..22
        WORD_KEY@18..19
          WORD@18..19 "2"
        SPACE@19..20 " "
        INTEGER@20..21
          NUMERAL@20..21 "2"
        NEWLINE@21..22 "\n"
      SPACE@22..25 "   "
      PREFIX_BLOCK@25..39
        WORD_KEY@25..26
          WORD@25..26 "c"
        SPACE@26..27 " "
        OPEN_BRACE@27..28 "{"
        NEWLINE@28..29 "\n"
        SPACE@29..31 "  "
        ENTRY@31..35
          WORD_KEY@31..32
            WORD@31..32 "3"
          SPACE@32..33 " "
          INTEGER@33..34
            NUMERAL@33..34 "3"
          NEWLINE@34..35 "\n"
        SPACE@35..37 "  "
        CLOSE_BRACE@37..38 "}"
        NEWLINE@38..39 "\n"
      SPACE@39..40 " "
      CLOSE_BRACE@40..41 "}"
      NEWLINE@41..42 "\n"
    SPACE@42..43 " "
    CLOSE_BRACE@43..44 "}"
    NEWLINE@44..45 "\n"
```

